comments: Adebayo (MIA) gives a step of distance when establishing himself in Wagner's (ORL) path and marginal contact occurs as the two engage and disengage while Adebayo turns to roll following the pick.
Carter Jr. (ORL) raises his arms to contest the driving shot attempt by Martin (MIA) and the contact is marginal.
Adebayo (MIA) gives a step of distance when establishing himself in Wagner's (ORL) path and marginal contact occurs during the pick.
Banchero (ORL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Carter Jr. (ORL) is raising his arm and contact occurs that affects Butler's (MIA) SQBR as he comes up through during the driving shot attempt.
Fultz (ORL) lifts and re-plants his right pivot foot prior to releasing the pass.
Adebayo (MIA) is turning slightly toward the basket and marginal contact occurs with Carter Jr. (ORL) following the screen.
There is no clear and conclusive camera angle that confirms if Strus (MIA) steps out of bounds.
Adebayo (MIA) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Carter Jr. (ORL) initiates contact with Adebayo (MIA) that dislodges him from his position as the screen is set.
Herro (MIA) avoids making body contact with Harris (ORL) as he contests the jump shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Wagner (ORL) initially attempts to avoid Adebayo (MIA) and Adebayo legally re-establishes himself in a screening position without delivering contact to Wagner or extending into his path.
Banchero (ORL) lifts and replants his left pivot foot prior to releasing his dribble.
Butler (MIA) moves forward into Banchero's (ORL) space during the close-out and initiates lower body contact that affects Banchero's ability to return to the floor.
Herro (MIA) establishes his left foot as his pivot and maintains it while stationary.
Carter Jr. (ORL) initiates contact with Butler (MIA) and dislodges him from his position.
Adebayo (MIA) comes slightly forward and Fultz (ORL) moves through marginal contact during his driving shot attempt.
Fultz (ORL) commits a take foul on Herro (MIA).
Strus (MIA) reaches for the rebound and marginal contact occurs with Fultz's (ORL) right arm.
Wagner (ORL) commits a take foul on Butler (MIA).
Anthony (ORL) steps into the plane of the 3-point line before Butler (MIA) releases his free throw attempt.
